These specially designed tools are perfect to maintain a healthy and attractive garden.

Garden tool is any tool made to make gardening easy, may it be hand tool or power tool. Get the real experience of gardening with right tool in your hand.Mini cultivator can be used for loosening of soil.

The handle color of this tool may vary depending on the availabilityMetal parts of this tool are coated for protection from rust and handle of this tool is specially designed for better grip.Blade Type: Fixed.
</p>
           

